reviewText: It's something to enjoy & for children to enjoy

$58? For TWO episodes of the Penguins TV series? Amazon shouldn't even allow this to be publicized. That's embarrassing. This is why places like Hastings are still in business. Pass on this, and buy a set like "New to the Zoo" or "Happy King Julien Day" for 1/10th of the price- for 8 episodes.
This is just two shorts from the TV series. 24 min runtime. They are funny and the kids love them.
